<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .home-link {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .home-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-link">Go to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>